#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Mutant Animals"
msgstr "變異動物"

#. ~ Description for Mutant Animals
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Expansion for animals that makes them evolve over time into new mutated "
"versions. Some of them, though, they are weird, become tameable, very "
"friendly, useful mutated versions. Some of them, however, whether they are "
"weird or not, become ferocious, grotesque, dangerous mutants."
msgstr ""
"動物擴展模組，使它們隨時間進化成新的變異版本。其中一些變得古怪、可馴服、非常友好且有用；另一些則無論是否古怪，都會變成兇猛、怪異且危險的突變體。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "songbird"
msgid_plural "songbirds"
msgstr[0] "鳴禽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'songbird'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid "A tiny bird with a noteable singing voice."
msgstr "一種以顯著歌喉著稱的小鳥。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "gargoyle"
msgid_plural "gargoyles"
msgstr[0] "石像鬼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gargoyle'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A flying mutant beast. It's unclear whether this is a bear that has grown "
"leathery wings or a bat that has grown to a massive size.  Either way, the "
"result is ugly and unfriendly."
msgstr "一種飛行的突變野獸。不清楚這是長出皮質翅膀的熊，還是體型巨大的蝙蝠。無論如何，結果都醜陋且不友好。"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "jacked rabbit"
msgid_plural "jacked rabbits"
msgstr[0] "壯碩兔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'jacked rabbit'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A wild hare that has grown to the size of a horse. Despite its bulk, this "
"mutant creature is incredibly fast-moving, capable of outrunning almost "
"anything alive.  If only you could put a saddle on it..."
msgstr "一種長到馬匹大小的野兔。儘管體型龐大，這種突變生物移動速度驚人，幾乎能超越任何活物。要是能給它裝上鞍具就好了……"

#: .\monsters.json
msgid "aerostatic octopod"
msgid_plural "aerostatic octopods"
msgstr[0] "浮空八爪魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'aerostatic octopod'}
#: .\monsters.json
msgid ""
"A mutant octopus floating on a bladder of lighter-than-air gas.  Due to its "
"inflated gas sac, it has the volume of a small car, but only has the mass as"
" a human. A curious creature, it has drifted in from the ocean to explore "
"dry land."
msgstr ""
"一種依靠輕於空氣的氣囊漂浮的突變章魚。由於膨脹的氣囊，其體積相當於一輛小型汽車，但質量僅如人類。這種好奇的生物從海洋漂流而來，探索乾燥的陸地。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant animal"
msgid_plural "mutant animals"
msgstr[0] "變異動物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant animal'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "Generic animal. Initial stats based off the groundhog."
msgstr "通用動物。初始屬性基於土撥鼠。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant tunneler"
msgid_plural "mutant tunnelers"
msgstr[0] "突變掘地獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant tunneler'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"A strange mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It tunnels "
"through the earth using spade-like teeth and long claws."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的奇怪突變生物。它利用鏟狀牙齒和長爪在地下掘洞穿行。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant runner"
msgid_plural "mutant runners"
msgstr[0] "突變疾行獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant runner'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"An odd mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  A set of long "
"spindly limbs carry its sleek form across the post apocalyptic landscape."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的奇特突變生物。它用一組細長的四肢，在末日後的荒原上拖曳著光滑的身軀移動。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant flyer"
msgid_plural "mutant flyers"
msgstr[0] "突變飛行獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant flyer'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"A weird mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It flies with its "
"arms and legs which have become twon sets of bat-like wings."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的怪異突變生物。它用已變成兩對蝙蝠狀翅膀的四肢飛行。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant swimmer"
msgid_plural "mutant swimmers"
msgstr[0] "突變游水獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant swimmer'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"A queer mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It has adapted to "
"life both in and out of water, having gills and fins, as well as two stubby "
"legs."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的奇異突變生物。它已適應水陸兩棲生活，擁有鰓和鰭，以及兩條粗短的腿。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant lurker"
msgid_plural "mutant lurkers"
msgstr[0] "突變潛行獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant lurker'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"A shy mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It lopes through the "
"night on a dozen tentacles terminating in sharp claws."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的害羞突變生物。它在夜間用十二根末端帶利爪的觸手蹣跚而行。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant swallower"
msgid_plural "mutant swallowers"
msgstr[0] "突變吞噬獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant swallower'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"A bizarre mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It snatches up "
"prey with its expansive mouth and traps it within a large translucent neck-"
"sack."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的離奇突變生物。它用其寬闊的大口攫取獵物，並將其困在一個巨大的半透明頸囊中。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant babler"
msgid_plural "mutant bablers"
msgstr[0] "突變呢喃獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant babler'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"An odd mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It makes weird "
"mumbling sounds as it prowls through the forests."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的奇特突變生物。它在森林中潛行時會發出怪異的咕噥聲。"

#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid "mutant gasser"
msgid_plural "mutant gassers"
msgstr[0] "突變噴氣獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant gasser'}
#: .\mutant_animals.json
msgid ""
"An odd mutated creature about the size of a large cat.  It emits a toxic gas"
" from spinal vents to ward off predators."
msgstr "一種體型如大貓般大小的奇特突變生物。它會從脊柱的排氣孔中釋放有毒氣體以驅趕捕食者。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "mutant songbird"
msgid_plural "mutant songbirds"
msgstr[0] "突變鳴禽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant songbird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "A mutant songbird that makes otherworldy music."
msgstr "一種能發出超凡脫俗音樂的突變鳴禽。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "mutant bird"
msgid_plural "mutant birds"
msgstr[0] "突變鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant bird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "A mutating bird."
msgstr "一隻正在突變的鳥。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "deformed bird chick"
msgid_plural "deformed bird chicks"
msgstr[0] "畸形雛鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deformed bird chick'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A sickly deformed bird chick.  If it survives it could mutate into something"
" even stranger."
msgstr "一隻病態的畸形雛鳥。如果它能存活下來，可能會突變成更奇怪的東西。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "malformed avian"
msgid_plural "malformed avians"
msgstr[0] "畸形禽類"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'malformed avian'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A mutating bird no longer capable of flight due to its twisted and "
"asymetrical wings."
msgstr "一隻正在突變的鳥，因其扭曲且不對稱的翅膀而無法再飛行。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "irradiated bird"
msgid_plural "irradiated birds"
msgstr[0] "輻射鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'irradiated bird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "A mutating bird afflicted with serious radiation burns."
msgstr "一隻遭受嚴重輻射灼傷的突變鳥。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "plague bird"
msgid_plural "plague birds"
msgstr[0] "瘟疫鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plague bird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "A mutating bird suffering from the symptoms of a flesh eating virus."
msgstr "一隻正遭受食肉病毒症狀折磨的突變鳥。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "two headed vultch"
msgid_plural "two headed vultchs"
msgstr[0] "雙頭禿鷲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'two headed vultch'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A mutated bird about the size of an eagle.  It has two featherless heads and"
" necks growing from its squat body.  The vultch can eject streams of sticky "
"bile when threatened."
msgstr "一種體型如鷹般大小的突變鳥。它矮胖的身體上長著兩個無毛的頭和脖子。這種禿鷲在受到威脅時可以噴射出粘稠的膽汁流。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "two headed chick"
msgid_plural "two headed chicks"
msgstr[0] "雙頭雛鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'two headed chick'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "A sickly deformed bird chick growing a second head."
msgstr "一隻病態畸形的雛鳥，長出了第二個頭。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "wing thing"
msgid_plural "wing things"
msgstr[0] "翼狀怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wing thing'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A mutated bird about the size of an albatross.  This monster is a grotesque "
"mass of writhing tentacles and blinking eyes.  Only its eight feathered "
"wings give any clue that it was once a common species of avian."
msgstr "一隻信天翁大小的變異鳥類。這怪物是一團扭曲觸手與眨動眼睛的怪誕聚合體。唯有其八隻羽翼暗示它曾是某種常見鳥類。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "iridescent bird"
msgid_plural "iridescent birds"
msgstr[0] "虹彩鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'iridescent bird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A mutated bird about the size of a goose.  A proud creature covered in "
"glittering feathers far more colorful than any parrot or peacock of the old "
"world.  Unlike other mutants, this bird is agreeable enough to be tamed."
msgstr "一隻鵝大小的變異鳥類。這隻驕傲的生物覆蓋著閃亮的羽毛，比舊世界的任何鸚鵡或孔雀都更加絢麗。與其他變異體不同，這種鳥性情溫順，可被馴服。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "ghoul bird"
msgid_plural "ghoul birds"
msgstr[0] "食屍鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ghoul bird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A mutated bird about the size of a crow.  Although primarily a scavenger, it"
" will attack agressively with a razor sharp beak capable of causing infected"
" bite wounds.  Its ability to digest rotting and tainted flesh makes it well"
" adapted to the current world."
msgstr "一隻烏鴉大小的變異鳥類。雖然主要食腐，但它會以能造成感染性咬傷的鋒利鳥喙發起兇猛攻擊。其消化腐爛與汙染肉類的能力使其能很好適應當前世界。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "elephant bird"
msgid_plural "elephant birds"
msgstr[0] "象鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'elephant bird'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A mutated bird about the twice size of an ostrich and with a similar shape."
"  Its beak has been replaced with a long sinuous trunk that can grab hold of"
" smaller creatures.  The elephant bird is highly territorial and aggressive."
msgstr "一隻體型兩倍於鴕鳥且外形相似的變異鳥類。其鳥喙被一條能抓握小型生物的長而蜿蜒的象鼻取代。象鳥具有強烈的領地意識且極具攻擊性。"

#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid "large deformed bird chick"
msgid_plural "large deformed bird chicks"
msgstr[0] "大型畸形雛鳥"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large deformed bird chick'}
#: .\mutant_birds.json
msgid ""
"A deformed bird chick already grown to the size of a turkey. How big will "
"this thing get?"
msgstr "一隻已長到火雞大小的畸形雛鳥。這東西究竟能長到多大？"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "mutant dog"
msgid_plural "mutant dogs"
msgstr[0] "變異犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant dog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "A mutating canine."
msgstr "一隻正在變異的犬科動物。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "mutant whelp"
msgid_plural "mutant whelps"
msgstr[0] "變異幼犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant whelp'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "A deformed and mutating canine whelp."
msgstr "一隻畸形且正在變異的幼犬。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "scab dog"
msgid_plural "scab dogs"
msgstr[0] "痂皮犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'scab dog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A mutating canine covered in scabs and bloody lesions.  Although weak from "
"disease, the animal is deranged and highly aggressive."
msgstr "一隻覆蓋著痂皮與血淋淋病灶的變異犬科動物。儘管因疾病而虛弱，但這動物精神錯亂且極具攻擊性。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "blister dog"
msgid_plural "blister dogs"
msgstr[0] "水皰犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blister dog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A mutating canine covered in giant blisters.  Although weak from disease, "
"the animal is deranged and highly aggressive."
msgstr "一隻覆蓋著巨大水皰的變異犬科動物。儘管因疾病而虛弱，但這動物精神錯亂且極具攻擊性。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "pus dog"
msgid_plural "pus dogs"
msgstr[0] "膿液犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'pus dog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A mutating canine with rancid pus dripping from its patchy fur.  Although "
"weak from disease, the animal is deranged and highly aggressive."
msgstr "一隻從其斑駁皮毛中滴下惡臭膿液的變異犬科動物。儘管因疾病而虛弱，但這動物精神錯亂且極具攻擊性。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "deformed whelp"
msgid_plural "deformed whelps"
msgstr[0] "畸形幼犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'deformed whelp'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "A mutating puppy with patchy fur and malformed limbs."
msgstr "一隻皮毛斑駁、四肢畸形的變異幼犬。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "worm dog"
msgid_plural "worm dogs"
msgstr[0] "蠕蟲犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'worm dog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A former canine mutated into a hairless monster with a thick tail and long "
"neck. Multifaceted eyes sprout irregularly atop its elongated skull."
msgstr "一隻由犬科動物變異而成的無毛怪物，擁有粗壯的尾巴與長頸。其細長的頭骨上不規則地生長著複眼。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "wormling"
msgid_plural "wormlings"
msgstr[0] "蠕蟲幼體"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wormling'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"The wriggling offspring of a worm dog. Multifaceted eyes sprout irregularly "
"atop its elongated skull."
msgstr "蠕蟲犬扭動著的後代。其細長的頭骨上不規則地生長著複眼。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "happysmile dog"
msgid_plural "happysmile dogs"
msgstr[0] "歡顏犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'happysmile dog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A former canine mutated into a skinless monster with an oversized head and "
"multiple rows of venomous fangs. Its absurdly wide mouth makes it appear to "
"have a permanent smile."
msgstr "一隻由犬科動物變異而成的無皮怪物，擁有過大的頭部與多排毒牙。其異常寬闊的嘴巴使其看起來永遠保持著笑容。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "happysmile puppy"
msgid_plural "happysmile puppys"
msgstr[0] "開心微笑幼犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'happysmile puppy'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"The chittering whelp of a happysmile dog. It has a permanent grin of "
"venomous fangs."
msgstr "開心微笑犬的吱喳幼崽。它長著毒牙構成的永久咧嘴笑容。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "digiridog"
msgid_plural "digiridogs"
msgstr[0] "迪吉里杜犬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'digiridog'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A former canine mutated into a weird creature with bone tubes growing from "
"its head and spine, from which it emits a stream of unearthly moans.  Its "
"oily blue saliva can prevent blood from clotting."
msgstr "由犬類變異而成的怪異生物，頭部和脊柱長出骨管，從中發出非塵世的呻吟聲。其油性的藍色唾液能阻止血液凝固。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "digiridog whelp"
msgid_plural "digiridog whelps"
msgstr[0] "迪吉里杜犬幼崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'digiridog whelp'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"The offspring of a digiridog. Its bone tubes are not yet developed and it "
"looks almost like a real dog."
msgstr "迪吉里杜犬的後代。其骨管尚未發育，看起來幾乎像真正的狗。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "direwolf"
msgid_plural "direwolfs"
msgstr[0] "恐狼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'direwolf'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"A canine mutated into a wild beast the size of a grizzly bear. It can "
"recover from disease and wounds with an alarming speed. The wild animal "
"cannot be controlled, but perhaps a younger version could be tamed."
msgstr "犬類變異為灰熊大小的野獸。它能以驚人的速度從疾病和傷口中恢復。這種野生動物無法被控制，但或許幼年個體可以被馴服。"

#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid "dire whelp"
msgid_plural "dire whelps"
msgstr[0] "恐狼幼崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dire whelp'}
#: .\mutant_canines.json
msgid ""
"The offspring of a direwolf, already the size of an actual wolf. It seems "
"almost as intelligent and friendly as a domestic dog."
msgstr "恐狼的後代，體型已如真正的狼一般大。它似乎與家犬一樣聰明和友好。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "cat"
msgid_plural "cats"
msgstr[0] "貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'cat'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "A deformed and mutating cat."
msgstr "一隻畸形且正在變異的貓。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "hairless cat"
msgid_plural "hairless cats"
msgstr[0] "無毛貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hairless cat'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid ""
"A mutating feline that has lost its coat of fur, making it appear weird and "
"sickly."
msgstr "一隻正在變異的貓科動物，失去了毛皮，使其看起來怪異且病態。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "multilimbed cat"
msgid_plural "multilimbed cats"
msgstr[0] "多肢貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'multilimbed cat'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid ""
"A mutating feline that has sprouted extra sets of vestigal legs and multiple"
" tails.  Its movements are slow and clumsy."
msgstr "一隻正在變異的貓科動物，長出了額外的幾組退化腿和多條尾巴。其動作緩慢而笨拙。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "venomous cat"
msgid_plural "venomous cats"
msgstr[0] "毒牙貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'venomous cat'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid ""
"A mutated feline that has acquired snake-like fangs and a powerful venom.  "
"It often hunts in packs making it more dangerous than its small size "
"suggests."
msgstr "一種獲得蛇狀毒牙和強效毒液的變異貓科動物。它常成群狩獵，使其比其小體型所暗示的更危險。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "vampire cat"
msgid_plural "vampire cats"
msgstr[0] "吸血貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vampire cat'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid ""
"A mutated feline grown to the size of a large dog.  It runs swiftly on six "
"legs and possesses razor sharp fangs."
msgstr "一種變異貓科動物，長到大狗般大小。它以六條腿快速奔跑，並擁有鋒利的尖牙。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "ink cat"
msgid_plural "ink cats"
msgstr[0] "墨汁貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ink cat'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid ""
"A dark mutated feline that hunts from the shadows.  It can spray a jet of "
"ink from its mouth to blind predators or prey."
msgstr "一種在陰影中狩獵的黑暗變異貓科動物。它能從口中噴射墨汁流，使捕食者或獵物失明。"

#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid "whip tongue"
msgid_plural "whip tongues"
msgstr[0] "鞭舌貓"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'whip tongue'}
#: .\mutant_felines.json
msgid ""
"A mutated feline grown to the size of a large dog.  Its fur has been "
"replaced with hard lizard-like scales and thorny knobs.  The cat has no eyes"
" but its long tongue continually sways back and forth tasting the air for "
"signs of prey."
msgstr "一種變異貓科動物，長到大狗般大小。其皮毛被堅硬的蜥蜴狀鱗片和多刺的瘤狀物取代。這隻貓沒有眼睛，但其長舌不斷來回擺動，品嚐空氣中的獵物跡象。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "fish"
msgid_plural "fish"
msgstr[0] "魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fish', 'str_pl': 'fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "A mutant fish.  The favorite prey of mutant cats and survivors."
msgstr "一種變異魚。是變異貓和倖存者最愛的獵物。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "puke fish"
msgid_plural "puke fish"
msgstr[0] "嘔吐魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'puke fish', 'str_pl': 'puke fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A disgustingly mutating fish about the size of a large carp.  It exudes a "
"gooey brown gel and smells like rotting milk."
msgstr "一種令人作嘔的變異魚，大小如大鯉魚。它滲出粘稠的棕色凝膠，聞起來像腐爛的牛奶。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "finger fish"
msgid_plural "finger fish"
msgstr[0] "手指魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'finger fish', 'str_pl': 'finger fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A freakishly mutating fish about the size of a large carp.  A cluster of "
"finger-like limbs have burst from its head."
msgstr "一種怪誕變異的魚，大小如大鯉魚。一簇手指狀的肢體從其頭部爆裂而出。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "tumor fish"
msgid_plural "tumor fish"
msgstr[0] "腫瘤魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tumor fish', 'str_pl': 'tumor fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"An odious mutating fish about the size of a large carp. It's so covered in "
"bleeding tumors and fleshy nodules that it can barely swim."
msgstr "一種令人作嘔的變異魚，體型約如大鯉魚。它渾身佈滿流血的腫瘤和肉質結節，幾乎無法遊動。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "angelic fish"
msgid_plural "angelic fish"
msgstr[0] "天使魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'angelic fish', 'str_pl': 'angelic fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A mutant fish about the size of a large carp.  Its internal organs glow with"
" a pulsing light which readily shines through its translucent skin."
msgstr "一種變異魚，體型約如大鯉魚。它的內臟發出脈動光芒，輕易透過半透明的皮膚顯現。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "bloatball fish"
msgid_plural "bloatball fish"
msgstr[0] "膨脹球魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloatball fish', 'str_pl': 'bloatball fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A mutant fish the size and shape of a basketball.  When threatened the fish "
"will inflate itself to massive size.  If attacked the fish and its attacker "
"will be caught in a violent explosion."
msgstr "一種變異魚，體型和形狀如籃球。受威脅時，魚會膨脹至巨大尺寸。若遭攻擊，魚和攻擊者將捲入劇烈爆炸。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "ghoul in the water"
msgid_plural "ghouls in the water"
msgstr[0] "水中的食屍鬼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ghoul in the water', 'str_pl': 'ghouls in the
#. water'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A large mutant fish the size of a tigershark.  It resembles a catfish but "
"instead of barbels it possess a pair of long spindly arms terminating in "
"disturbingly human hands.  The ghoul grabs prey on the water's edge and "
"pulls it into the deep."
msgstr "一種大型變異魚，體型如虎鯊。它形似鯰魚，但觸鬚處有一對細長手臂，末端是令人不安的人手。食屍鬼抓住水邊的獵物，將其拖入深水。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "jawed terror"
msgid_plural "jawed terrors"
msgstr[0] "顎骨恐怖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'jawed terror'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A large mutant fish the size of a tigershark.  It has a massive set of jaws "
"lined with razor-sharp teeth."
msgstr "一種大型變異魚，體型如虎鯊。它擁有巨大的顎部，佈滿鋒利的牙齒。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "accordian fish"
msgid_plural "accordian fish"
msgstr[0] "手風琴魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'accordian fish', 'str_pl': 'accordian fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A mutant fish the size of a carp.  It moves by strangely extending and "
"contracting its body, giving it its odd name."
msgstr "一種變異魚，體型如鯉魚。它通過奇怪地伸縮身體移動，因此得此怪名。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "whisperwill"
msgid_plural "whisperwills"
msgstr[0] "低語鰩"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'whisperwill'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A large mutant fish the size of a tiger shark.  Its body is long and sleek "
"like that of an eel.  The whisperwill can perfectly mimic any human whose "
"flesh it has consumed, and will call out for help with the voices of the "
"dead."
msgstr "一種大型變異魚，體型如虎鯊。身體長而光滑，似鰻魚。低語鰩能完美模仿任何它吞噬過的人類，並用死者的聲音呼救。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "butter fish"
msgid_plural "butter fish"
msgstr[0] "黃油魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'butter fish', 'str_pl': 'butter fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A mutant fish the size of a carp.  It controls its bouyancy by producing and"
" releasing a thick oil which might be harvestable."
msgstr "一種變異魚，體型如鯉魚。它通過產生和釋放濃稠油脂來控制浮力，這種油脂或許可採集。"

#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid "spitter fish"
msgid_plural "spitter fish"
msgstr[0] "噴水魚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spitter fish', 'str_pl': 'spitter fish'}
#: .\mutant_fish.json
msgid ""
"A mutant fish the size of a carp.  It hunts by squirting jets of water at "
"passing birds and knocking them into the water."
msgstr "一種變異魚，體型如鯉魚。它通過向經過的鳥類噴射水柱，將其擊落水中來捕獵。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "mutant snake"
msgid_plural "mutant snakes"
msgstr[0] "變異蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant snake'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "A mutating snake."
msgstr "一條正在變異的蛇。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "molting snake"
msgid_plural "molting snakes"
msgstr[0] "蛻皮蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'molting snake'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid ""
"A mutating snake shedding its dried epidermis.  Although vulnerable and "
"weak, this snake still has a venomous bite."
msgstr "一條正在變異並蛻去幹燥表皮的蛇。雖然脆弱且虛弱，此蛇仍具毒咬能力。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "jaculus"
msgid_plural "jaculi"
msgstr[0] "標槍蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'jaculus', 'str_pl': 'jaculi'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid ""
"A mutated snake grown to the size of a python.  It can launch itself at its "
"prey by uncoiling its body like a giant spring."
msgstr "一條變異蛇，已長至蟒蛇大小。它能像巨型彈簧般展開身體，彈射向獵物。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "bone snake"
msgid_plural "bone snakes"
msgstr[0] "骨蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bone snake'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid ""
"A mutated snake grown to the size of python.  Bone plates cover its body and"
" it bites with a hard beak as well as venomous fangs."
msgstr "一條變異蛇，已長至蟒蛇大小。骨板覆蓋其身體，它用堅硬的喙和毒牙咬擊。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "frostbite snake"
msgid_plural "frostbite snakes"
msgstr[0] "凍傷蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'frostbite snake'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid ""
"A mutated snake armed with a powerful poison.  Its bite causes flesh to "
"wither and die, similar to a case of frostbite."
msgstr "一條攜帶強力毒液的變異蛇。其咬傷會導致肉體枯萎死亡，類似凍傷症狀。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "devil frog"
msgid_plural "devil frogs"
msgstr[0] "魔鬼蛙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'devil frog'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid ""
"A mutated bullfrog with jagged teeth and horms.  Its bright red skin is said"
" to produce hallucinagenic toxins."
msgstr "一種變異的牛蛙，長有鋸齒狀牙齒和角。其鮮紅的皮膚據說能產生致幻毒素。"

#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid "gamma-toad"
msgid_plural "gamma-toads"
msgstr[0] "伽馬蟾蜍"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gamma-toad'}
#: .\mutant_reptiles.json
msgid ""
"A common toad that has mutated into a huge radioactive monstrosity.  It "
"pulses with heat, energy, and malice."
msgstr "一隻普通蟾蜍變異而成的巨大放射性怪物。它散發著熱量、能量與惡意。"

#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid "mutant rat"
msgid_plural "mutant rats"
msgstr[0] "變異鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant rat'}
#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid "A worm-tailed rodent with long whiskers and beady eyes."
msgstr "一種長著蠕蟲般尾巴、長鬚和珠子般眼睛的齧齒動物。"

#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid "plague rat"
msgid_plural "plague rats"
msgstr[0] "瘟疫鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plague rat'}
#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid "A mutant rat that carries one or more dangerous diseases."
msgstr "攜帶一種或多種危險疾病的變異鼠。"

#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid "piranha rat"
msgid_plural "piranha rats"
msgstr[0] "食人鼠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'piranha rat'}
#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid ""
"A mutant rat with a powerful set of sharp teeth.  Not that dangerous on its "
"own, but deadly in a swarm."
msgstr "一種長著鋒利牙齒的變異鼠。單獨一隻並不危險，但成群結隊時則致命。"

#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid "rat creature"
msgid_plural "rat creatures"
msgstr[0] "鼠怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rat creature'}
#: .\mutant_rodents.json
msgid ""
"A mutant rat that has impossibly crossbred with a spider and grown to the "
"size of a wolf.  It has venomous mandibles and numerous eyes."
msgstr "一種變異鼠，不可思議地與蜘蛛雜交，長到了狼一般大小。它長有毒顎和眾多眼睛。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant cow"
msgid_plural "mutant cows"
msgstr[0] "變異奶牛"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant cow calf"
msgid_plural "mutant cow calfs"
msgstr[0] "變異牛犢"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "twisthorn cow"
msgid_plural "twisthorn kine"
msgstr[0] "扭角牛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'twisthorn cow', 'str_pl': 'twisthorn kine'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating cow with mutiple horns bursting from its skull at odd angles.  "
"Its skin has dried and contracted, causing a network of bloody cracks to "
"cover the unfortunate animal.  Due to extreme pain, the cow is violent and "
"agitated."
msgstr ""
"一頭正在變異的奶牛，多隻角以怪異的角度從顱骨中爆出。它的皮膚乾燥收縮，佈滿血痕裂紋，覆蓋著這頭不幸的動物。由於極度痛苦，這頭牛變得狂暴而焦躁。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "blubber cow"
msgid_plural "blubber kine"
msgstr[0] "肥脂牛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blubber cow', 'str_pl': 'blubber kine'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating cow so weighed down by fat and blubber that it can barely move.  "
"It's unlikely this easy meal will survive for long in the post cataclysmic "
"wastes. It will produce no milk, but you can wait and see if it mutates into"
" something useful..."
msgstr ""
"一頭正在變異的奶牛，因脂肪和肥膘過重而幾乎無法移動。這頓美餐不太可能在災後廢土中存活太久。它不會產奶，但你可以等待，看它是否會變異成有用的東西……"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "ironthorn cow"
msgid_plural "ironhorn kine"
msgstr[0] "鐵角牛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ironthorn cow', 'str_pl': 'ironhorn kine'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutated cow that has somehow grown a pair of metal horns which it can use "
"to great effect.  It is a highly aggressive animal."
msgstr "一頭變異的奶牛，不知何故長出了一對金屬角，並能有效利用。它是一種極具攻擊性的動物。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "ironhorn calf"
msgid_plural "ironhorn calves"
msgstr[0] "鐵角牛犢"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ironhorn calf', 'str_pl': 'ironhorn calves'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "A young mutated cow with a pair of metal horns."
msgstr "一頭年輕的變異奶牛，長著一對金屬角。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "auroch"
msgid_plural "auroch"
msgstr[0] "原牛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'auroch', 'str_pl': 'auroch'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutated cow that has evolved back into its prehistoric state.  It has "
"grown larger and has a shaggy coat of thick fur.  Unlike most mutants, this "
"beast still has the potential to be tamed."
msgstr "一頭變異奶牛，已進化回其史前狀態。它體型更大，長有濃密的粗毛。與大多數突變體不同，這頭野獸仍有被馴服的潛力。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "auroch calf"
msgid_plural "auroch calves"
msgstr[0] "原牛犢"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'auroch calf', 'str_pl': 'auroch calves'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "A young mutated cow that has evolved back into its prehistoric state."
msgstr "一頭年輕的變異奶牛，已進化回其史前狀態。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "moss bison"
msgid_plural "moss bison"
msgstr[0] "苔蘚野牛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'moss bison', 'str_pl': 'moss bison'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutated cow that can photosynthesize sunlight through its moss-like fur.  "
"This green beast is quite lethargic and is often mistaken for a bush or "
"hedge."
msgstr "一頭變異的奶牛，能通過苔蘚般的皮毛進行光合作用。這頭綠色野獸相當嗜睡，常被誤認為是灌木或樹籬。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "moss bison calf"
msgid_plural "moss bison calves"
msgstr[0] "苔蘚野牛犢"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'moss bison calf', 'str_pl': 'moss bison calves'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A young mutated cow that can photosynthesize sunlight through its moss-like "
"fur.  This green beast is quite lethargic and is often mistaken for a bush "
"or hedge."
msgstr "一頭年輕的變異奶牛，能通過苔蘚般的皮毛進行光合作用。這頭綠色野獸相當嗜睡，常被誤認為是灌木或樹籬。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant deer"
msgid_plural "mutant deers"
msgstr[0] "變異鹿"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "crying hind"
msgid_plural "crying hinds"
msgstr[0] "哀鳴雌鹿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crying hind', 'str_pl': 'crying hinds'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating deer covered in lesions dripping pus and fluid.  The animal "
"frequently lets out sorrowful cries of pain."
msgstr "一隻變異鹿，渾身佈滿流膿滲液的病灶。這動物時常發出痛苦的哀嚎。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "burnt hart"
msgid_plural "burnt hart"
msgstr[0] "焦灼雄鹿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'burnt hart', 'str_pl': 'burnt hart'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating deer badly burnt by radiation and heat.  It's hide is blackened "
"with ash and crusted with dried blood."
msgstr "一隻因輻射與高溫嚴重灼傷的變異鹿。它的皮毛被灰燼燻黑，並結著乾涸的血痂。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant horse"
msgid_plural "mutant horses"
msgstr[0] "變異馬"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "famine mare"
msgid_plural "famine mares"
msgstr[0] "饑荒母馬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'famine mare'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating horse almost dead from starvation. It's skeleton is visible under"
" its stretched hide. You can attract it with food if you'd like to see if it"
" will mutate into something useful..."
msgstr "一隻因飢餓瀕死的變異馬。它的骨架在緊繃的皮下清晰可見。如果你想看看它是否會變異成有用的東西，可以用食物吸引它……"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "glue horse"
msgid_plural "glue horses"
msgstr[0] "膠水馬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glue horse'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating horse that oozes a sticky substance from pulsing pores.  Driven "
"mad by this affliction, the horse scratches itself against trees and "
"buildings, leaving traces of disgusting glue everywhere it goes."
msgstr "一匹從搏動毛孔滲出粘稠物質的變異馬。這種折磨使它發狂，馬匹在樹木和建築上摩擦自己，所到之處留下噁心的膠痕。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant sheep"
msgid_plural "mutant sheep"
msgstr[0] "變異綿羊"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "naked sheep"
msgid_plural "naked sheep"
msgstr[0] "裸體綿羊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'naked sheep', 'str_pl': 'naked sheep'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating sheep that has lost all of its wool to radiation sickness, making"
" it look weird and sickly."
msgstr "一隻因輻射病失去全部羊毛的變異綿羊，看起來怪異而病態。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "gamma sheep"
msgid_plural "gamma sheep"
msgstr[0] "伽馬綿羊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'gamma sheep', 'str_pl': 'gamma sheep'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating sheep swollen with radioactive gas, which it occasionally "
"releases into its surroundings."
msgstr "一隻因放射性氣體腫脹的變異綿羊，它會偶爾向周圍釋放這些氣體。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "glass creature"
msgid_plural "glass creatures"
msgstr[0] "玻璃生物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'glass creature'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutated ungulate whose flesh and bones have become almost completely "
"transparent.  This natural camoflauge makes it difficult to see at a "
"distance or at night."
msgstr "一種變異有蹄動物，其血肉骨骼幾乎完全透明。這種天然偽裝使它在遠處或夜間難以被察覺。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant unicorn"
msgid_plural "mutant unicorns"
msgstr[0] "變異獨角獸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'mutant unicorn'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A rare mutated ungulate with a single horn growing from its forehead, making"
" it look somewhat like the mythical animal.  This unicorn, however, is not "
"so friendly."
msgstr "一種罕見的變異有蹄動物，前額長有單角，使其看起來有點像神話中的生物。但這隻獨角獸並不那麼友好。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "screech creature"
msgid_plural "screech creatures"
msgstr[0] "尖嘯生物"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'screech creature'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutated ungulate that has grown an extra pair of legs and a long giraffe-"
"like neck.  It can defend itself by spitting globs of foul smelling mucus "
"and letting out ear-shattering screams."
msgstr "一種變異有蹄動物，長出了額外的腿和長頸鹿般的脖子。它能通過吐出惡臭黏液團和發出震耳欲聾的尖叫來自衛。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "screeching brat"
msgid_plural "screeching brats"
msgstr[0] "尖嘯幼崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'screeching brat', 'str_pl': 'screeching brats'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A juvenile mutated ungulate that has grown an extra pair of legs and a long "
"giraffe-like neck.  It can defend itself by spitting globs of foul smelling "
"mucus and letting out ear-shattering screams."
msgstr "一隻幼年變異有蹄動物，長出了額外的腿和長頸鹿般的脖子。它能通過吐出惡臭黏液團和發出震耳欲聾的尖叫來自衛。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "sleipnir"
msgid_plural "sleipnir"
msgstr[0] "斯萊普尼爾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sleipnir', 'str_pl': 'sleipnir'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A prodigious mutated horse with a third pair of legs. Despite its size, it's"
" capable of running far faster than a normal horse. It appears to not mind "
"human company."
msgstr "一匹非凡的變異馬，擁有第三對腿。儘管體型龐大，它卻能跑得比普通馬快得多。它似乎不介意人類的陪伴。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "sleipnir foal"
msgid_plural "sleipnir foals"
msgstr[0] "斯萊普尼爾幼駒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sleipnir foal', 'str_pl': 'sleipnir foals'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A young mutated horse with a third pair of legs. It appears to not mind "
"human company."
msgstr "一匹年輕的變異馬，擁有第三對腿。它似乎不介意人類的陪伴。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant pig"
msgid_plural "mutant pigs"
msgstr[0] "變異豬"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "mutant piglet"
msgid_plural "mutant piglets"
msgstr[0] "變異豬崽"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "fly-blown pig"
msgid_plural "fly-blown pigs"
msgstr[0] "蠅蛆豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'fly-blown pig'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating pig infested with fly larva. It can barely see or move due to its"
" necrotic wounds."
msgstr "一隻感染蠅蛆的變異豬。由於壞死傷口，它幾乎看不見也無法移動。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "tumor pig"
msgid_plural "tumor pigs"
msgstr[0] "腫瘤豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tumor pig'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A mutating pig that has inflamed tumors all over its body. It looks to be in"
" constant pain and distress."
msgstr "一隻全身長滿發炎腫瘤的變異豬。它看起來持續處於痛苦與煎熬之中。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "rhino pig"
msgid_plural "rhino pigs"
msgstr[0] "犀角豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rhino pig'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A large mutated pig that has grown a thick protective hide similar to that "
"of a rhino."
msgstr "一隻大型變異豬，長出了類似犀牛的厚實防護皮。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "rhino piglet"
msgid_plural "rhino piglets"
msgstr[0] "犀角豬崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rhino piglet'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A juvenile mutated pig that is growing a thick protective hide similar to "
"that of a rhino."
msgstr "一隻幼年變異豬，正在長出類似犀牛的厚實防護皮。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "quill pig"
msgid_plural "quill pigs"
msgstr[0] "刺針豬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'quill pig'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid ""
"A large mutated pig with rows of venomous quills growing from its spine.  "
"Despite it's fearsome appearance, it is fairly non aggressive."
msgstr "一隻大型變異豬，其脊柱上長出了一排排有毒的刺針。儘管外表駭人，它卻相當溫順。"

#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "quill piglet"
msgid_plural "quill piglets"
msgstr[0] "刺針豬崽"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'quill piglet'}
#: .\mutant_ungulates.json
msgid "A juvenile mutated pig covered in small bone nubs."
msgstr "一隻覆蓋著小骨突的幼年變異豬。"

